Then later after the episode is over and Chris Hardwick is doing the “tribute to those who died” thingy it showed Dan’s cereal. A dear food, that will never be forgotten. summary:
I feel like Daniel Howell's smile and personality are underrated.
That's not to say that Phil isn't a ball of sunshine. I'll be...
body:
I feel like Daniel Howell’s smile and personality are underrated.

That’s not to say that Phil isn’t a ball of sunshine. I’ll be the first to tell you he is. I mean look at him. He’s a total smol (giant) bean.

But then there’s Dan.

He has such a lovely smile that has the power of the sun in terms of energy and motivation. His personality is golden. Look at this smol (also giant) bean.

(Tap or click to enlarge)

Now, I love Phil. I’ll say it again.

But this is a Daniel Howell appreciation post. More pics are in order here.

I included a link here to a vid that further expresses my thoughts.

Okay. Now that we have that out of the way, have a nice night/day!

And don’t forget our beatiful boi!
